OL,3,CMigrants expected to face tougher
OL,4,CEnglish standards and longer residency
OL,5,Cwaits
OL,7,FMigrants may have to learn a higher
OL,8,Fstandard of English to work in the UK
OL,9,Fand wait for longer before they can
OL,10,Fsettle permanently, reports have
OL,11,Fsuggested.
OL,13,FAn immigration White Paper due to be
OL,14,Fpublished next week is expected to set
OL,15,Fout the reforms, as Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fgets tougher on migration in the wake
OL,17,Fof Labour's local election losses to
OL,18,FReform UK.
