OL,3,CMigrants expected to face tougher
OL,4,CEnglish standards and longer residency
OL,5,Cwaits
OL,7,FAmong the strict new measures under
OL,8,Fconsideration is raising English
OL,9,Flanguage proficiency required by
OL,10,Fmigrants applying for a UK work visa,
OL,11,Faccording to The Times.
OL,13,FThey would in future be required to
OL,14,Fhave the equivalent of a foreign
OL,15,Flanguage A-level standard of English,
OL,16,Frather than the GCSE standard
OL,17,Fcurrently required, the newspaper said.
