OL,3,CMigrants expected to face tougher
OL,4,CEnglish standards and longer residency
OL,5,Cwaits
OL,7,FElsewhere, the Financial Times (FT)
OL,8,Freported that migrants will be
OL,9,Frequired to wait as long as 10 years
OL,10,Fbefore they can apply for indefinite
OL,11,Fleave to remain in the UK.
OL,13,FMost migrants who come to Britain on
OL,14,Ftime-limited work visas can currently
OL,15,Fmake an application for indefinite
OL,16,Fleave to remain after five years.
OL,18,FThis paves the way for them to apply
OL,19,Ffor benefits and the path towards UK
OL,20,Fcitizenship.
