OL,5,Cwaits
OL,7,FThe wait could be extended to 10 years
OL,8,Fif migrants have spent too much time
OL,9,Foutside the UK since arriving or if
OL,10,Fthere are questions about their
OL,11,Ffinancial status, the FT said.
OL,13,FSimilar plans to extend the waiting
OL,14,Fperiod for indefinite leave to remain
OL,15,Fwere set out by the Conservatives on
OL,16,FTuesday.
