OL,5,Cwaits
OL,7,FBoth the Tories' "Deportation Bill"
OL,8,Fand Labour's plans to toughen its
OL,9,Fmigration response come as both
OL,10,Fparties aim to win back voters from
OL,11,FNigel Farage's Reform UK.
OL,13,FThe party, which has positioned itself
OL,14,Fas tough on migration, won hundreds of
OL,15,Flocal council seats and wrested
OL,16,Fcontrol of the Runcorn and Helsby
OL,17,Fparliamentary constituency from Labour
OL,18,Fon May 1.
